{"tid":332864,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 穿 緊 身 衣 自 比 蜘 蛛 俠","createTime":"2017-07-23T10:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T10:52:35.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"add71cacd2f290f15d9296abdf1905d41e5f6750","tid":332864,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"藝人從來都不易做，坤哥吳業坤就因為拍攝無綫新劇《誇世代》而要在大熱天時，成32度高溫兼烈日當空之下着上長袖緊身衣，曬到他連雙眼也幾乎睜不開，真係隔住個mon都覺得熱。坤哥就上載了這張相上facebbok，留言表示：「當你有機會穿上緊身衣，你可以幻想自己是蜘蛛俠或蝴蝶俠。」熱成咁都仲有心情搞笑。不過相中的坤哥其實又不算肥，當然就一定無蜘蛛俠咁fit，但坤哥都起碼無肚腩，線條都ok結實，算見得下人㗎。有網民就笑指他：「好在，都仲有線條！」亦有不少網民戥他辛苦，叫他加油為他打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/721147/xlarge/11402f2e66c72b44217765645a49541c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F721147%2Fxlarge%2F11402f2e66c72b44217765645a49541c.jpg&h=a9a7c4ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35854b7045bc268fc2bbb04f76f431bcdb673fde","tid":332864,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"個天又幾靚"},{"pid":"4a2265394a601e681a4bbd3231c29f431751ccc3","tid":332864,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個天又幾靚</blockquote><br />\nCut走條友就靚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ea4acd41583e1bed5f9ab3938dc1c1437d838a","tid":332864,"uid":14797,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/184156_d80784b4cceb0b24b09db41edc52b4a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F184156_d80784b4cceb0b24b09db41edc52b4a0.jpg&h=bf5e9eb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df18885161fa721f692a9ee2b3359e7af93ae704","tid":332864,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:52:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}